Using req.params.id
QUESTION 2 OF 16
CORRECT
On a controller how can I get the ID on a route like: "/user?id=123"
Using req.query.id
QUESTION 3 OF 16
CORRECT
What's the difference between a method="post" and method="get" on an form
method="get" sends the data of the form on the url and method="post" sends it hidden from the user
